sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner as Data Owner
    participant Frontend as React SPA
    participant Backend as FastAPI
    participant Worker as Celery Worker
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Qdrant as Qdrant

    Owner->>Frontend: Upload reference images
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/v1/images (owner scope)
    Backend->>DB: INSERT images, segments
    DB-->>Backend: image_id, segment_ids
    Backend->>Worker: enqueue segmentation + extraction

    Worker->>Qdrant: upsert vectors + payload
    Qdrant-->>Worker: indexed
    Worker->>DB: UPDATE segments (qdrant_point_id)
    Worker-->>Backend: indexing complete

    Backend->>DB: UPDATE data_update_status
    DB-->>Backend: updated
    Backend-->>Frontend: index status response
    Frontend-->>Owner: Reference data indexed

    Owner->>Frontend: Trigger re-index
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/v1/index
    Backend->>Qdrant: rebuild collection
    Qdrant-->>Backend: re-index complete
    Backend-->>Frontend: re-index result
    Frontend-->>Owner: Qdrant refreshed
